  <span id="freeText12955678357335025651" style="display:none"><i>The Yellow Birds</i> wins the 2012 <a href="https://apps.facebook.com/theguardian/books/2012/nov/29/guardian-first-book-award-2012-kevin-powers" rel="nofollow noopener">Guardian First Book Award</a>! Review can now be found at <a href="http://tinyurl.com/cket9jg" rel="nofollow noopener">Expendable Mudge Muses Aloud</a>!<br /><br /><a href="https://www.imdb.com/title/tt3739110/?ref_=nv_sr_srsg_0" rel="nofollow noopener">The 2017 film</a> stars Alden Ehrenreich as Bartle, gets a solid 4 stars of five from me, and is available free to Amazon Prime members.</span>
