<span id="freeTextContainer4769938490943448927">Let me tell you right now that this book is going to hurt.<br/><br/> The suffering the Iraqi War veterans endure in this book will touch a raw spot in you that you might prefer not to experience.<br/><br/> You will probably, like me, have a lump in your throat and teary eyes most of the time when reading this excellent first novel by Kevin Powers. 5 stars all around and I&apos;m looking forward to reading all future books by Powers, a combat veteran of the Iraq war.</span>
  <span id="freeText4769938490943448927" style="display:none">Let me tell you right now that this book is going to hurt.<br /><br /> The suffering the Iraqi War veterans endure in this book will touch a raw spot in you that you might prefer not to experience.<br /><br /> You will probably, like me, have a lump in your throat and teary eyes most of the time when reading this excellent first novel by Kevin Powers. 5 stars all around and I'm looking forward to reading all future books by Powers, a combat veteran of the Iraq war.</span>
